WEBVTT

00:01:58.094 --> 00:02:02.396
But it is still socially acceptable
to publicly vilify women as such,

00:02:02.420 --> 00:02:06.054
because none of these reasons
have made it into the social narrative.

00:02:06.482 --> 00:02:12.165
When I was little and learning
about the inevitability of maternity,

00:02:12.189 --> 00:02:13.932
it was never explained to me

00:02:13.956 --> 00:02:17.987
the commonness of these factors
that women consider,

00:02:19.718 --> 00:02:22.131
like the risk of passing on
hereditary illness,

00:02:22.155 --> 00:02:25.313
the danger of having to stop
life-saving medication

00:02:25.337 --> 00:02:27.276
for the duration of your pregnancy,

00:02:27.300 --> 00:02:29.428
concern about overpopulation,

00:02:29.452 --> 00:02:31.214
your access to resources,